Required attribution
--------------------
The model is fine-tuned on training data that is itself CC-BY-4.0. When you use
or redistribute the model, retain this attribution:

  Trained on "Svensk fraktur 1626-1816", Språkbanken Text, University of
  Gothenburg (digitisation: Gothenburg University Library; transcription:
  GREPECT), https://doi.org/10.23695/5sme-7437, licensed CC-BY-4.0.

The base model "german_print" (Weil, Kamlah & Schmidt 2023,
https://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10519596) is released under CC0-1.0; no
attribution is legally required for it, but it is credited as good practice.
